node.text:
Struggling with writer's block, a novelist finds inspiration when she meets a down-on-his-luck oddball who constantly changes personas and alter egos to cope with the past and avoid reality.

With: @ilizasheslinger @davidkoechner @cleopatracoleman @trezzo_ @nickthune #ad #therightonemovie

node.title: Watch “The Right One” now on iTunes and ON Demand 🙏🥰💖

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'African Doll @igetloudtf Sis, do yourself a favor & learn to walk away. When the communication start to fade, when he getting disrespectful, & mistreating you, you gotta let go & move on tor the better. Don't waste your energy trying to force something that isn't meant to be. Love isn't enough sometimes!'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'lex personally don't like to explain what's wrong with me.. i'd rather jus lay low until i feel better and start feeling like myself again. i don't like to bother people. don't even like people.'.
